article.description: — Isiah Dasher scored 17 points to lead St. Peter's to a 65-57 win over Canisius on Tuesday.
article.headline: Dasher scores 17 to lift St. Peter's over Canisius 65-57
article.linkText: Dasher scores 17 to lift St. Peter's over Canisius 65-57
article.story: JERSEY CITY, N.J. -- — Isiah Dasher scored 17 points to lead St. Peter's to a 65-57 win over Canisius on Tuesday. KC Ndefo had 12 rebounds and four blocks for St. Peter's (6-6, 4-1 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Scott Hitchon had 14 points and eight rebounds for the Golden Griffins (5-12, 1-5). Malek Green added 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
